folder: Franklin Avenue & Wallabout Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Franklin Avenue, east side, at Wallabout Street, looking north. On the right, at the southeast corner, is the Donohue Boiler Works; at the northeast corner is the Tole Morgan optical
instruments factory.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1941
